    "updated_at": "2015-01-16T12:21:52Z",
    "body": "This approach is made harder by the fact rustdoc test driver depends on `get_unstable_features_settings()`. This means that to use the proposed approach not only two versions of rustc, but also two versions of rustdoc have to be built.\n\n(alternatively two versions of librustc_driver can be built)\n",
