    "updated_at": "2015-01-16T22:51:42Z",
    "body": "The issue of whether it can be worked around does not really matter to me - if people really want to cheat then it's in their hands.\n\nIt seems more complicated to me to teach the build system to build a second driver than to do what we're presently doing.\n\nCan you tell me how it broke snapshots?\n",
